{"tid":1622091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疑染伊波拉病毒54歲港人曾到剛果　留醫瑪嘉烈　現時情況穩定","createTime":"2019-10-04T15:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:23:58.000Z","uid":204220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b07d5f9cbe68294a5a7d64a5c113d82cfc6ca6","tid":1622091,"uid":204220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"衞生署衞生防護中心今日（4日）接獲一宗埃博拉（伊波拉）病毒病懷疑個案的呈報，該名54歲女病人為香港人，曾於今年5月至9月到訪剛果民主共和國金沙薩，自昨日起出現頭痛、暈眩、發燒、嘔吐和腹瀉，同日到瑪嘉烈醫院急症室求醫，隨即入院接受隔離治療，現時情況穩定。病人的血液樣本初步檢驗對伊波拉病毒呈陰性反應，惟按世衞指引，衞生防護中心會安排病人於兩天後，接受血液覆檢，以排除病人感染伊波拉病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e490832178545669437128bdf39e35f94217d6","tid":1622091,"uid":204220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"今日就爆伊波拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3707c0d03efd618611ef0d0cd7404f2c5990658c","tid":1622091,"uid":204220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"呢單要睇實！"},{"pid":"7a7d0d61cb617ebbfe5ff63be0c0cf05b6a04c59","tid":1622091,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"陰性"},{"pid":"f1dc33b38bf3b9c97b028d6e20cef40c46a5002b","tid":1622091,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"無來源連結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />忽然 咁怪 有d咁既野"},{"pid":"a7b76175a0d1681e977bf8d0ca5bbdcfe3c9952b","tid":1622091,"uid":204220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1dc33b38bf3b9c97b028d6e20cef40c46a5002b","tid":1622091,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"無來源連結<img src=\"/assets/fac